criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients aged 18 years or older;

          -  Be able to read Chinese and use a mobile phone;

          -  Histologically or cytologically confirmed solid tumor;

          -  Diagnosed chronic cancer pain

          -  Could understand the study process and evaluation, agreed to participate in the trial,
             and signed the informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Illiterate person;

          -  Incompetence;

          -  Inability to complete the pain assessment;

          -  Participation in any other therapies or other study protocols that may have an impact
             on pain intensity, which were the main outcomes of this study.
